<div class="example-sec pb-4" data-controller="scroll-showcase">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="card-box p-8 mb-8 sticky top-20 z-30">
      <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 text-[#E06540]">
        Example Project Walkthrough
      </h4>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="text-left">
          <p class="font-medium text-lg mb-6 text-gray-800">
            Want to make a cool project and earn shells? Here's how it works:
          </p>

          <ul class="font-normal text-base space-y-3 text-gray-600">
            <li class="step-item transition-all duration-500 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-transparent hover:bg-gray-50 cursor-pointer"
                data-scroll-showcase-target="step"
                data-step="1"
                data-action="click->scroll-showcase#goToStep">
              <span class="font-medium">1.</span> Brainstorm a cool idea
            </li>
            <li class="step-item transition-all duration-500 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-transparent cursor-pointer"
                data-scroll-showcase-target="step"
                data-step="2"
                data-action="click->scroll-showcase#goToStep">
              <span class="font-medium">2.</span> Build your project, make it awesome
            </li>
            <li class="step-item transition-all duration-500 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-transparent cursor-pointer"
                data-scroll-showcase-target="step"
                data-step="3"
                data-action="click->scroll-showcase#goToStep">
              <span class="font-medium">3.</span> Share devlogs to get others excited
            </li>
            <li class="step-item transition-all duration-500 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-transparent cursor-pointer"
                data-scroll-showcase-target="step"
                data-step="4"
                data-action="click->scroll-showcase#goToStep">
              <span class="font-medium">4.</span> Ship your project and get shells
            </li>
            <li class="step-item transition-all duration-500 p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-transparent cursor-pointer"
                data-scroll-showcase-target="step"
                data-step="5"
                data-action="click->scroll-showcase#goToStep">
              <span class="font-medium">5.</span> Watch as other people vote on your project for bonuses!
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="relative">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-center mb-4">
            <button data-scroll-showcase-target="back"
                    data-action="click->scroll-showcase#prevStep"
                    class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transform hover:scale-105 opacity-50">
              <span class="font-medium">Back</span>
            </button>

            <span class="text-sm font-medium text-gray-600 bg-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full border">
              Step <span data-scroll-showcase-target="stepIndicator">1</span> of 5
            </span>

            <button data-scroll-showcase-target="next"
                    data-action="click->scroll-showcase#nextStep"
                    class="flex items-center px-4 py-2 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 disabled:opacity-50 disabled:cursor-not-allowed transform hover:scale-105">
              <span class="font-medium">Next</span>
            </button>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-yellow-100 to-amber-100 rounded-xl transition-all duration-500 shadow-lg overflow-hidden" data-scroll-showcase-target="preview">
            <div class="transition-all duration-300" data-scroll-showcase-target="imageContainer">
              <img src="https://files.catbox.moe/3t37wi.png"
                   alt="Project step 1"
                   class="w-full h-auto transition-all duration-500"
                   data-scroll-showcase-target="image">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
